lead_paragraph: In the midst of arguably their finest team performance in a quadrennium, a familiar nemesis provided the U.S. men's gymnastics team with a reminder that nothing comes easily.

headline.print_headline: Americans Solid 2nd to China in Gymnastics Preliminaries
